msContents.summary: A group of works on Peripatetic, or Aristotelian, philosophy, including logic, physics, mathematics, and some limited astrology.

supportDesc.extent: 287 leaves : 192 x 157 mm. bound to 202 x 159 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 287 leaves; contemporary pagination in ink, 1-288, 1-186, [v], 1-3, [iii], 7-60, 1-16, [iv], upper outer corners; modern pagination in pencil, [i-iv, 1-560], lower outer corners.

binding.p: Contemporary pigskin with lettering H[ans] G[eorg] V[on] K[önigsfeld] 1645 (Zacour-Hirsch).
